{
  "stem": "21626.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I mustn't make it sound-- sound too negative, because there were many very kind and good people there who were instrumental in my rehabilitation, in a sense.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I made some wonderful, wonderful friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were very few family members that survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My grandmother actually died when the Gestapo arrested Auntie Bertha and took her into prison.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that was prior to her going to the camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Grandmother-- the shock of it killed grandmother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Grandfather died in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He went deranged through the conditions which were there, and which he had to meet at such an old age.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And all the other relatives, of course, had similar fates.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There was one cousin, my cousin, who survived, who was 10 years older than I-- Heda.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Heda Bloch-- was called, the maiden name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then she was called Heda Margolius.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She married her sweetheart after the war, who also survived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he was an eminent lawyer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Well, the Nazis didn't get him, but the Communist government executed him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So she lost her husband under the communists.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So she didn't have a very good time of it either.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then there was a distant cousin of my fathers, who found me through my book when it was-- when my autobiography was published in the States.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And she'd been looking for me vainly for years and years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she was a survivor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So, you know, there weren't many of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And there were-- we were a very, very, large family, as most Jewish families were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But I wanted to just tell you, very briefly, about what repercussions these-- housing-- housing us child refugees with the war societies had.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "There was one young lad from our school, a year younger than me, so he was barely 16, if that.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
